window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Same town. Different school. New secret.</b></p> <p>One night was all it was supposed to be. No names, no numbers, no strings. I didn't expect to ever see him again—or for that night to leave me with a permanent reminder. But life has a funny way of ruining plans.</p> <p>Now, I'm back in Sun Valley, face-to-face with Emilio Chavez, the Devil who once made me forget all the rules. He's furious I disappeared without a word, and he's made it his mission to make me pay. It's only a matter of time before he uncovers my biggest secret. When he does, it could ruin everything.</p> <p>But Emilio isn't the kind of guy to walk away—not from me, and not from the little boy with his eyes.</p> <p>In a town where football is life, Emilio Chavez will have to decide what matters most: his dreams or the family he never saw coming.</p>"; 
